  "description": "<i>Pro Striker 2</i> is the sequel to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/pro-striker\">the first title</a>, and is a very similar soccer game to the previous year's model. The updates are largely cosmetic, with the game retaining the same top-down view and field minimap. Of course, the full 1994 J.League team and player roster is included. The exhibition, playoff, and league modes are back from the first game, as well as the all-star mode that was added in <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/pro-striker-perfect\">its update</a>. Once again, up to four players can play simultaneously, and the menu system has also been greatly streamlined.",
